{"tid":2514430,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［韓劇］大發不動產","createTime":"2021-05-03T09:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T13:40:28.000Z","uid":36040,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7aa4999f8c484a7425dc5128537207935a91f1","tid":2514430,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRtRmkBKMS9PwnauUhFMiTUimqRvVis3VXRejDUa1xrGc?filename=Vae1bvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVae1bvb.jpg&h=c4627138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《大發不動產》（韓語：대박부동산／大박不動產，英語：Sell Your Haunted House），為韓國KBS2於2021年4月14日起播出的水木連續劇，由《赤身的消防員》、《學校2017》的朴珍錫導演與河秀真、李英華和鄭妍書編劇合作打造。此劇講述一位不動產經紀人將鬼神出沒或者人死後離開的房產進行驅魔，將其淨化的靈異奇幻故事。<br />\n<br />\n主演：張娜拉，鄭容和<br />\n<br />\n香港由Viu自4月14日起每週三、四深夜上線。"},{"pid":"c50d99e603d354ac84d4ef6564dc9ebfc8e7d754","tid":2514430,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"套劇唔錯幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊邊睇邊傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aea7d1947f5755a8381677d5fe299d9defc7390","tid":2514430,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"估唔到要青頭先做得靈媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f184a8295d95c2edfd74e0fb3af46aaa23524e","tid":2514430,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:14:20.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"95f67b77be0bd8b67ddbf974e1cc6782251a283c","tid":2514430,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:15:45.000Z","msg":"好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" clas